				<td colspan="2"><span>Can confirm you can target mobs behind and to the side of you in 3rd person view. I use this technique when swarming in Nadox using only rs3. What you have to do is set up the Toggle Target Hot-key in your Options. Once in 3rd person view, as long as you've panned out far enough and can see the mobs from your view, you can target them.
<br />
